          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">Gear Module (m) = P.C.D. (mm)  ∕  number-of-teeth</text><text styleclass="Interface" translate="true">.</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> </text></para>
